

French rail network disruption
There are reports of disruption across main line train services affecting Eurostar services and domestic high speed trains in several parts of France. French railways state that services could be disrupted until Monday 29 July and are advising travellers to postpone travel if possible. Check with your travel operator, or railway operatorâ€™s website, including:
